_sText:
An idea like this popped into my head the other, so I figured 'What the hell, I'll try it'. It took me 2 days, but this is the end result.



 Two teams start at each end of the elevator shaft. Ladders and a stairwell connect both of those ends. This map is mainly close quarters.


 It isn't exactly bot friendly. The terrorist team tend to stay on their spawn floor and the counter-terrorist team tend to hop down to the 3rd floor and shoot at every breakable object they see.


 2 Easter eggs are hidden in the map. Let me know if you find them :D


 Enjoy playing and please don't hesitate to give constructive criticism. It's the only way I can get better.
